{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da2-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2431k"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2431k"},"text":"§ 2431k.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual reports to Congress","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than April 15 of each year, the President shall prepare and transmit to the Congress an annual report concerning the operation of the Facility for the prior calendar year. Such report shall include—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da3-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2431k/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a description of the activities undertaken by the Facility during the previous calendar year;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da4-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2431k/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a description of any Agreement entered into under this subchapter;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da5-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2431k/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a report on any Funds that have been established under this subchapter and on the operations of such Funds; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2431k/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a description of any grants that have been provided by administering bodies pursuant to Agreements under this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8fc09da7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. V, § 813, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/214/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–214, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-07-29"},"text":"July 29, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/893"},"text":"112 Stat. 893","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/440/s10"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–440, § 10","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-01-14"},"text":"Jan. 14, 2019","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/5584"},"text":"132 Stat. 5584","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8fc09da8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8fc09da9-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id8fc09daa-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Prior sections 2432 to 2435 were repealed by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/329/tIV/s413/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–329, title IV, § 413(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/761"},"text":"90 Stat. 761","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2432, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. V, § 802, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/189/s24"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–189, § 24","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/728"},"text":"87 Stat. 728","children":[],"tail":", authorized appropriation of $504,000,000 for fiscal year 1974 to remain available until expended for relief and reconstruction of South Vietnam, Cambodia, and Laos."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2433, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. V, § 803, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/189/s24"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–189, § 24","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/728"},"text":"87 Stat. 728","children":[],"tail":", provided for assistance to South Vietnamese children."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2434, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. V, § 804, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/189/s24"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–189, § 24","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/729"},"text":"87 Stat. 729","children":[],"tail":", made provision for assistance to the Center for Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery in Saigon."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 2435, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. V, § 806, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/559/s41"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–559, § 41","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-12-30"},"text":"Dec. 30, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1812"},"text":"88 Stat. 1812","children":[],"tail":", directed that provisions covering special programs for relief of South Vietnam, Cambodia, and Laos not apply to programs related to population growth, narcotics control, humanitarian programs by international organizations, and regional programs."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id8fc09dab-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/440"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–440","children":[],"tail":" struck out subsec. (a) designation and heading, substituted “April 15” for “December 31” and, in two places, “calendar year” for “fiscal year”, and struck out subsec. (b). Prior to amendment, text of subsec. (b) read as follows: “Not later than December 15 of each year, each member of the Board shall be entitled to receive a copy of the report required under subsection (a). Each member of the Board may prepare and submit supplemental views to the President on the implementation of this subchapter by December 31 for inclusion in the annual report when it is transmitted to Congress pursuant to this section.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id8fc09dac-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"delegationOfFunctions","id":"id8fc09dad-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"t